{"tid":1143960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲女觀塘搭的士 被座位針筒刺傷臀","createTime":"2019-05-08T00:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T00:53:55.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2c707b7994bb665ec3acd312c9a02163865d8d","tid":1143960,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ridD9uF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FridD9uF.png&h=26a1c280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合醫院。<br />\n<br />\n一名姓羅30歲女子，昨傍晚6時許在觀塘偉業街，登上一輛的士前往馬鞍山，其間她感到臀部疼痛，並在的士後座發現一支約4吋長的針筒。她通知的士司機，前往聯合醫院求醫及報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列作襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"45518e6f92e28bf04ec6ebd9bdb0333b149afb8a","tid":1143960,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:21:28.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2234e745e78a97e5cd10683f63bf986b46122afd","tid":1143960,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:21:40.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"8590df7ccae65deecdea7627aec132c1095b6588","tid":1143960,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"愛滋病人+1"},{"pid":"bbd6fed801311f63fdd7b73d121365ab8624805d","tid":1143960,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:25:24.000Z","msg":"的士針灸師"},{"pid":"96dfbda13771fd041526821381e6d989f0508c07","tid":1143960,"uid":13375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"N"},{"pid":"fa7293fb699f50c1f41ef08c271c202885fe5887","tid":1143960,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234f432ec1e490e2e9e91b22e0b1168afa4bc16e","tid":1143960,"uid":6